                "title": "Response Spectrum Analysis",
                "lesson": "IS 1893 provides 5 % damped spectra for rock, medium & soft soils. RSA combines modal responses by SRSS or CQC. For torsionally irregular buildings, accidental eccentricity of ± 5 % of building dimension is added.",
